      <title>玻利维亚的繁荣已转向萧条，助长了总统不太可能的东山再起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-23/bolivia-s-dollar-crisis-pits-evo-morales-against-luis-arce-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯·阿尔塞总统对抑制通货膨胀感到自豪。但一场酝酿已久的金融危机使这一标志性成就面临风险，可能为他从导师转型为竞争对手的埃沃·莫拉莱斯(Evo Morales)开辟道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-23/bolivia-s-dollar-crisis-pits-evo-morales-against-luis-arce-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将堕胎斗争推向特朗普在佛罗里达州的地盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/election-2024-biden-campaigns-on-abortion-in-florida-while-trump-on-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将注意力集中在美国最严格的堕胎法之一上，在唐纳德·特朗普自己的佛罗里达州地盘上抓住这​​个问题，而他的对手则因刑事审判而分心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/election-2024-biden-campaigns-on-abortion-in-florida-while-trump-on-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨表示欧盟银行需要有能力在欧盟范围内转移资本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/scholz-says-eu-banks-need-ability-to-move-capital-across-bloc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，欧盟的银行应该能够在整个欧盟范围内自由转移资本，这呼应了该行业许多高管的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/scholz-says-eu-banks-need-ability-to-move-capital-across-bloc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:13:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国逮捕极右翼政党助手，罪名是为中国从事间谍活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-arrests-aide-to-far-right-party-for-spying-for-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德累斯顿警方拘留了一名涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动的德国公民。据 ARD 报道，该男子是欧洲议会选举中极右翼选择党的主要候选人马克西米利安·克拉赫 (Maximilian Krah) 的雇员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-arrests-aide-to-far-right-party-for-spying-for-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士冻结超过 140 亿美元的俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士冻结了在该国持有的130亿瑞士法郎（143亿美元）的俄罗斯资产，其中包括俄罗斯央行超过70亿瑞士法郎的储备和资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:10:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国赤字上升刺激借贷增加，减税希望落空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-budget-deficit-overshoots-in-setback-for-hunt-s-tax-cut-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府上一财年的预算缺口超出了预期，促使计划进一步举债，并凸显了财政大臣杰里米·亨特在大选前减税时面临的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-budget-deficit-overshoots-in-setback-for-hunt-s-tax-cut-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
